    "content_hash": "dc7249a9bc846415",
    "department": "VIP",
    "description": "ABOUT THE COMPANY\n\nThrill Labs is the driving force behind Thrill.com http://Thrill.com — a next-generation crypto gaming platform built to deliver a customer focused experience. Our mission is to build the world’s biggest gaming brand, combining cutting-edge technology, bold creativity, and a deep respect for our players.\n\nBacked by a world-class team and launching at an exciting stage of growth, we’re redefining what premium gaming looks like in a crypto-native world.\n\n\nABOUT THE ROLE\n\nAt Thrill.com http://Thrill.com, our VIP players are at the heart of everything we do.\n\nWe’re looking for a VIP Host to join Thrill at a pivotal moment — someone who thrives on building relationships, delivering white-glove experiences, and creating genuine loyalty with our most valuable players.\n\nAs one of the early VIP Hosts at Thrill, you’ll help shape how we engage, retain, and grow our high-value player base globally. You’ll act as the trusted point of contact for VIPs, delivering a deeply personalized experience while balancing player satisfaction, sustainability, and long-term value.\n\nThis role sits at the intersection of hospitality, analytics, and crypto-native customer experience — and offers real ownership in defining what “best-in-class VIP” means at Thrill.\n\n\nWHAT YOU’LL BE DOING\n\n\nVIP RELATIONSHIP MANAGEMENT\n\n - Own and manage a portfolio of high-value VIP players globally\n\n - Serve as the primary point of contact, delivering proactive, high-touch, personalized service\n\n - Build trusted, long-term relationships through consistent and meaningful engagement\n\n - Handle escalations and complex player needs with confidence and care\n\n\nPLAYER GROWTH \u0026 RETENTION\n\n - Identify and onboard high-potential players into Thrill’s Host program\n\n - Design and execute tailored engagement, retention, and reactivation strategies\n\n - Manage promotional and incentive budgets responsibly, balancing value creation with profitability\n\n - Drive key VIP KPIs including engagement, retention, and lifetime value\n\n\nINSIGHTS \u0026 COLLABORATION\n\n - Analyze player behavior, trends, and performance to inform decision-making\n\n - Track portfolio health, churn risk, and ROI using CRM tools and dashboards\n\n - Share structured player insights with Product, Marketing, Payments, and Compliance teams to improve the overall player experience\n\n\nVIP EXPERIENCES\n\n - Support the planning and execution of exclusive online and offline VIP experiences\n\n - Assist with bespoke gifting, promotions, and events that reinforce Thrill’s premium brand\n\n\nRESPONSIBLE GAMING \u0026 COMPLIANCE\n\n - Operate in full alignment with Thrill’s Responsible Gaming standards\n\n - Identify and escalate risk behaviors appropriately\n\n - Ensure all VIP activity adheres to internal controls, promotional guidelines, and compliance requirements\n\n\n\n\n\nWHAT YOU’LL NEED\n\n\nEXPERIENCE\n\n - 1–3+ years experience in a high-touch, customer-facing role within iGaming\n\n - Strong understanding of online gaming, casino products, and player behavior\n\n - Comfort working in fast-paced, high-growth environments\n\n\nSKILLS\n\n - Excellent written and verbal communication skills in English\n\n - Strong analytical mindset with the ability to interpret player data and trends\n\n - Experience using CRM tools, dashboards, and modern communication platforms\n\n - Ability to manage multiple priorities while delivering consistently high standards\n\n\nCRYPTO-NATIVE MINDSET\n\n - Solid understanding of cryptocurrency fundamentals (wallets, transactions, blockchain basics)\n\n - Comfortable engaging with crypto-native users across global time zones\n\n\nPERSONAL ATTRIBUTES\n\n - Player-first, relationship-driven mindset\n\n - Commercially aware — understands how to balance incentives with sustainable growth\n\n - Detail-oriented, organized, and proactive\n\n - Calm, confident, and solutions-focused under pressure\n\n - Willingness to work non-traditional hours, including evenings and weekends\n\n - Open to occasional travel for VIP events (approx. 20–25%)\n\n\nBONUS POINTS FOR\n\n - Experience in crypto casinos, sportsbooks, or Web3 products\n\n - Multilingual capabilities\n\n - Experience working in remote-first teams\n\n\nWHY JOIN US?\n\nAt Thrill Labs, you won’t just manage VIP players — you’ll help define how premium crypto gaming is done.\n\nYou’ll have the opportunity to:\n\n - Shape the VIP function from the ground up\n\n - Work alongside a world-class, ambitious team\n\n - Make a real impact at launch-stage scale\n\n - Help build a globally loved gaming brand\n\nIf you’re excited by ownership, fast growth, and delivering unforgettable player experiences — we’d love to hear from you.",
    "employment_type": "FullTime",
    "is_active": true,
